Description: Egypt, pair of adult males walking along city street in Alexandria. Wearing shoes, gowns, head-gear, one carrying shut umbrella. Three-storey European buildings at right, European adult males walking at left and right. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
